--*** BeforeChangeValue EXTRAPOLATION {MLK@2011} -- 1. 100/SupplyCapacity = TonerProSeite(ideal) update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set BefChValue_extrapol = BeforeChangeValue-(100/convert(decimal(7,2),SupplyCapacity))*(case when coleranttype='black' then (case when isnull(d_ZaehlerGesamt_dead,0)<>0 then isnull(d_ZaehlerGesamt_dead,0)-AfterChange_DeadVolume else -1 end) else (case when isnull(d_ZaehlerFarbe_dead,0)<>0 then isnull(d_ZaehlerFarbe_dead,0)-AfterChange_DeadVolume else -1 end) end ) from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where BeforeChangeValue>0 and SupplyCapacity>0 and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4
-- 2. TonerProSeite Update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set BefChValue_TPS_Real = BeforeChangeValue- TonerProSeite*(case when coleranttype='black' then (case when isnull(d_ZaehlerGesamt_dead,0)<>0 then isnull(d_ZaehlerGesamt_dead,0)-(100.00-AfterChangeValue)/TonerProSeite else 0 end) else (case when isnull(d_ZaehlerFarbe_dead,0)<>0 then isnull(d_ZaehlerFarbe_dead,0)-(100.00-AfterChangeValue)/TonerProSeite else 0 end) end) from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where TonerProSeite<>0 and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4
Update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set BefChValue_TPS_LinR = BeforeChangeValue- TonerProSeite_linR*(case when coleranttype='black' then (case when isnull(d_ZaehlerGesamt_dead,0)<>0 then isnull(d_ZaehlerGesamt_dead,0)-(100.00-AfterChangeValue)/TonerProSeite else 0 end) else (case when isnull(d_ZaehlerFarbe_dead,0)<>0 then isnull(d_ZaehlerFarbe_dead,0)-(100.00-AfterChangeValue)/TonerProSeite else 0 end) end) from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where TonerProSeite<>0 and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4
-- 3. TonerProTag Update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set BefChValue_TPD_Real = BeforeChangeValue- TonerProTag*(DATEDIFF(dd,BeforeChangeDate,AfterChangeDate)-(100.00-AfterChangeValue)/TonerProTag) from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where TonerProTag<>0 and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4
update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set BefChValue_extrapol = BefChValue_TPS_Real where BefChValue_TPS_Real<BeforeChangeValue and BefChValue_TPS_Real>0 and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4
-- 4. Korrektur wenn BefChValue_extrapol nicht annehmbare Werte angenommen hat! Update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set BefChValue_extrapol = BeforeChangeValue from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4 and (BefChValue_extrapol> BeforeChangeValue or BefChValue_extrapol<0 or BefChValue_extrapol is null)
--*** HIER ORIGNAL BeforeCHANGDate aus Supplies_WS_SQL einlesen!!!
--*** CHANGEDATE EXTAPOLATION {MLK@2011} --***** Extrapolation des ChangeDatums = BeforChangeDate + "DATE ((Zaehler(BeforChangeDate) + (BeforeChangeValue-BefChValue_extrapol)/TonerProSeite(real oder ideal))" --***** BEDINGUNG: BeforeChangeDate >= ChangeDate_extrapol <= AfterChangeDate -- *** 1. TonerProSeite(ideal) = 100.00/SupplyCapacity update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set ChangeDate_extrapol= CASE WHEN Coleranttype ='black' THEN (Select MIN(b.Datum) from STAT_TonerZaehler b where a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 and b.IDNR=a.IDNR and b.Zaehler_Gesamt>= ((Select c.Zaehler_Gesamt from STAT_TonerZaehler c where a.Ebene1=c.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=c.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=c.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=c.Ebene4 and c.IDNR=a.IDNR and c.Datum=a.BeforeChangeDate) +(a.BeforeChangeValue-a.BefChValue_extrapol)/100.00*a.SupplyCapacity)) ELSE (Select MIN(b.Datum) from STAT_TonerZaehler b where a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 and b.IDNR=a.IDNR and b.Zaehler_Farbe>= ((Select c.Zaehler_Farbe from STAT_TonerZaehler c where a.Ebene1=c.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=c.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=c.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=c.Ebene4 and c.IDNR=a.IDNR and c.Datum=a.BeforeChangeDate) +(a.BeforeChangeValue-a.BefChValue_extrapol)/100.00*a.SupplyCapacity)) END from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange a where a.SupplyCapacity>1 and a.Ebene1=:1 and a.Ebene2=:2 and a.Ebene3=:3 and a.Ebene4=:4
-- *** 2. TonerProSeite (real) update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set ChangeDate_extrapol= CASE WHEN Coleranttype ='black' THEN (Select MIN(b.Datum) from STAT_TonerZaehler b where a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 and b.IDNR=a.IDNR and b.Zaehler_Gesamt>= ((Select c.Zaehler_Gesamt from STAT_TonerZaehler c where a.Ebene1=c.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=c.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=c.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=c.Ebene4 and c.IDNR=a.IDNR and c.Datum=a.BeforeChangeDate) +(a.BeforeChangeValue-a.BefChValue_extrapol)/a.TonerProSeite)) ELSE (Select MIN(b.Datum) from STAT_TonerZaehler b where a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 and b.IDNR=a.IDNR and b.Zaehler_Farbe>= ((Select c.Zaehler_Farbe from STAT_TonerZaehler c where a.Ebene1=c.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=c.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=c.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=c.Ebene4 and c.IDNR=a.IDNR and c.Datum=a.BeforeChangeDate) +(a.BeforeChangeValue-a.BefChValue_extrapol)/a.TonerProSeite)) END from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange a where a.TonerProSeite>0 and a.Ebene1=:1 and a.Ebene2=:2 and a.Ebene3=:3 and a.Ebene4=:4 -- *** 3. ChangeDate_extrapol = BeforechangeDate wenn BeforeChangeValue=BefChValue_extrapol update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set ChangeDate_extrapol= BeforeChangeDate from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where BeforeChangeValue=BefChValue_extrapol and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4 -- *** 4. restliche ChangeDate_extrapol-Werte, die auÃŸerahlb der BEDINGUNG liegen "einnorden" update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set ChangeDate_extrapol= CASE WHEN ChangeDate_extrapol<BeforeChangeDate THEN BeforeChangeDate ELSE AfterChangeDate-1 END from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where ChangeDate_extrapol not between BeforeChangeDate and AfterChangeDate and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4 -- *** 5. ChangeDate_extrapol-Werte, die gleich AfterChangeDate sind auf AfterChangDate+1 setzen {MLK@2012} update STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set ChangeDate_extrapol= AfterChangeDate-1 from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange where ChangeDate_extrapol= AfterChangeDate and Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4
Update dbo.STAT_TonerZaehlerChange set ChangeDate_Previous = ( Select CASE WHEN ( Select c.ChangeDate_extrapol from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange c where c.Ebene1=a.Ebene1 and c.Ebene2=a.Ebene2 and c.Ebene3=a.Ebene3 and c.Ebene4=a.Ebene4 and c.IDNR=a.IDNR and a.Coleranttype=c.Coleranttype and c.ChangeDate_extrapol= ( Select MAX(b.ChangeDate_extrapol) from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange b where b.ChangeDate_extrapol<a.ChangeDate_extrapol and a.Coleranttype=b.Coleranttype and a.IDNR=b.IDNR and a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 ) ) is null THEN (Select b.PreviousAfterChangeDate from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange b where b.ChangeDate_extrapol=a.ChangeDate_extrapol AND a.Coleranttype=b.Coleranttype and a.IDNR=b.IDNR and a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4)
ELSE (Select c.ChangeDate_extrapol from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange c where c.Ebene1=a.Ebene1 and c.Ebene2=a.Ebene2 and c.Ebene3=a.Ebene3 and c.Ebene4=a.Ebene4 and c.IDNR=a.IDNR and a.Coleranttype=c.Coleranttype and c.ChangeDate_extrapol= (Select MAX(b.ChangeDate_extrapol) from STAT_TonerZaehlerChange b where b.AfterChangeDate<a.AfterChangeDate and a.Coleranttype=b.Coleranttype and a.IDNR = b.IDNR and a.Ebene1=b.Ebene1 and a.Ebene2=b.Ebene2 and a.Ebene3=b.Ebene3 and a.Ebene4=b.Ebene4 ) ) END) FROM dbo.STAT_TonerZaehlerChange a where a.Ebene1=:1 and a.Ebene2=:2 and a.Ebene3=:3 and a.Ebene4=:4
